  - Properties: `Id`, `CustomerId`, `InvoiceNumber`, `IssuedAt`, `SubTotal`, `ServiceChargeAmount`, `DiscountTotal`, `GrandTotal`, `LoyaltyDiscountApplied`, `PaymentStatus`, `PaymentMethod`, `AmountPaid`, `DueDate`, `CreatedByStaffId`, `Notes`, `ServiceAppointmentId`, `PartsStockDeducted`, `KhaltiPaymentIdx`
  - Loyalty constants: `LoyaltyThreshold = 5000m`, `LoyaltyDiscountRate = 0.10m`
